{
  "stem": "895.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They have-- they speak a normal Dutch, with a little Jordaan accent, you know, like-- they were good.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they tried to help the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had a fight with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was too small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But after the war, they made a big statue of the uprising in February, in 1941, in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And what happened in Amsterdam, when I-- when I went to the shul, I have-- we still have our place there, going back to 1530-- our own place, in Amsterdam, in the Spanish and Portuguese synagogue-- belongs to our family.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We opened the door there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I found half the books here, all of them gold outside-- Jesserun de Pinto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there, I went in shul every Saturday on the same place and sat there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And who comes walking in but my father-in-law-- from my first wife.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was interned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When the war broke out, the British consul went to his place, where he was making shoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they said, Ziff, you've got to come with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We're moving away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All the English people are moving out of here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Take the family.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He said, my business-- well, he should have gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, after that, he was captured by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was interned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He went to Vittel, in France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's where they-- he survived to the intern camp with his second wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he came in the shul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He heard I was living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was living in Scotland, but he came all the way here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he said he's coming back next week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He commits suicide in Scotland, in Glasgow, because he saw that his grandchildren and his daughter was dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
